{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"group-supporting","type":"group","x":-60,"y":0,"width":2120,"height":660,"label":"Supporting Tables"},
		{"id":"group-core-tables","type":"group","x":-60,"y":-720,"width":1560,"height":660,"label":"Core Content Tables"},
		{"id":"group-display","type":"group","x":-60,"y":720,"width":2120,"height":360,"label":"Display Surfaces ‚Äî what actually gets shown"},
		{"id":"group-pipeline","type":"group","x":-60,"y":-1020,"width":2120,"height":240,"label":"Pipeline Stages (auto-dispatch chain)"},
		{"id":"stage-scrape","type":"text","text":"## 1. Scrape\n`ProcessChapterPipeline`\n\nScrapes HTML ‚Üí `<p>` tags\n\n**Writes**:\n`raw_content` (immutable)","x":0,"y":-1000,"width":280,"height":200,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"stage-preprocess","type":"text","text":"## 2. Preprocess\n`ProcessChapterPipeline`\n\nRules: exclusion, cleaning,\ntable detection\n\n**Writes**:\n`processed_content`\n`is_table_row`, `table_data`","x":340,"y":-1000,"width":280,"height":200,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"stage-p1","type":"text","text":"## 3. LLM Pipeline 1\nCharacter Association\n`ProcessChapterCharactersWithLlm`\n\n**Writes**:\n`chapter_character_appearances`\nCreates new `novel_characters`","x":680,"y":-1000,"width":280,"height":200,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"stage-p2","type":"text","text":"## 4. LLM Pipeline 2\nDialogue Attribution\n`ProcessChapterWithLlm`\n\n**Writes**:\n`llm_processed_paragraphs`\n`speaker_id`, `is_dialogue`","x":1020,"y":-1000,"width":280,"height":200,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"stage-p3","type":"text","text":"## 5. LLM Pipeline 3\nNarrative Analysis\n`ProcessChapterNarrativeWithLlm`\n\n**Writes**:\n`chapter_summaries`\nkey_events, spoiler_level","x":1360,"y":-1000,"width":280,"height":200,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"stage-tts","type":"text","text":"## 6. TTS Generation\n`GenerateChapterTts` ‚Üí chronicle-tts\n\n**Reads**: `llm_processed_paragraphs`\n(multi-voice) OR `processed_content`\n(single-voice fallback)\n\n**Writes**: `chapter_tts`\nUploads mp4 audio to S3","x":1700,"y":-1000,"width":360,"height":200,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"t-novels","type":"text","text":"## `novels`\n\n| Column | Type |\n|--------|------|\n| id | bigint PK |\n| title | string |\n| author | string? |\n| publisher | string? |\n| status | string? |\n| year | int? |\n| genres | jsonb |\n| tags | jsonb |\n| rating_value | decimal(3,1)? |\n| rating_count | int? |\n| cover_image_url | text? |\n| read_url | text? |\n| **source_url** | text UNIQUE |\n| source | string |\n| created_at | timestamp |\n| updated_at | timestamp |","x":0,"y":-700,"width":320,"height":540,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"t-summaries","type":"text","text":"## `chapter_summaries`\n\n| Column | Type |\n|--------|------|\n| id | bigint PK |\n| **chapter_id** | FK UNIQUE ‚Üí novel_chapters |\n| summary | text? |\n| key_events | jsonb |\n| characters_present | jsonb |\n| spoiler_level | varchar(20) |\n| llm_model | varchar? |\n| processed_at | timestamp? |\n| created_at | timestamp |\n| updated_at | timestamp |","x":1680,"y":-700,"width":380,"height":440,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"t-chapters","type":"text","text":"## `novel_chapters`\n\n| Column | Type |\n|--------|------|\n| id | bigint PK |\n| **novel_id** | FK ‚Üí novels |\n| chapter_key | string? |\n| chapter_index | int? |\n| title | string |\n| read_url | text? |\n| **llm_character_status** | varchar(50) |\n| llm_character_processed_at | timestamp? |\n| **llm_processing_status** | varchar(50) |\n| llm_processed_at | timestamp? |\n| **llm_narrative_status** | varchar(50) |\n| llm_narrative_processed_at | timestamp? |\n| created_at | timestamp |\n| updated_at | timestamp |\n\n*Status values:*\n`pending` / `complete` / `failed`","x":380,"y":-700,"width":360,"height":640,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"t-paragraphs","type":"text","text":"## `novel_chapter_paragraphs` ‚≠ê\n\n| Column | Type |\n|--------|------|\n| id | bigint PK |\n| **chapter_id** | FK ‚Üí novel_chapters |\n| order | uint |\n| **raw_content** | text ‚Äî immutable scraped |\n| **processed_content** | text ‚Äî after rules |\n| excluded | bool |\n| table_group_id | uint? |\n| **is_table_row** | bool |\n| **is_section_header** | bool |\n| **table_data** | jsonb? |\n| created_at | timestamp |\n| updated_at | timestamp |\n\n---\n> üì± **Flutter Reader** displays `processed_content`\n> üîä **TTS (single-voice)** reads `processed_content`\n> ‚öÝÔ∏è LLM text lives in a SEPARATE table","x":800,"y":-700,"width":380,"height":640,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"t-llm-paras","type":"text","text":"## `llm_processed_paragraphs` ‚≠ê\n\n| Column | Type |\n|--------|------|\n| id | bigint PK |\n| **paragraph_id** | FK ‚Üí novel_chapter_paragraphs |\n| original_order | uint |\n| **split_order** | uint (0 if unsplit) |\n| **content** | text ‚Äî LLM segment text |\n| **speaker_id** | FK ‚Üí novel_characters? |\n| **is_dialogue** | bool |\n| **is_narration** | bool |\n| table_validated | bool? |\n| is_artifact | bool |\n| artifact_reason | varchar? |\n| llm_model | varchar? |\n| llm_request_id | varchar? |\n| processed_at | timestamp? |\n| created_at | timestamp |\n| updated_at | timestamp |\n\n---\n> üîä **TTS (multi-voice)** reads `content` + `speaker_id`\n> One source paragraph ‚Üí **1 or more** LLM rows\n> (split when dialogue + attribution mixed)","x":1240,"y":-700,"width":380,"height":640,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"t-characters","type":"text","text":"## `novel_characters`\n\n| Column | Type |\n|--------|------|\n| id | bigint PK |\n| **novel_id** | FK ‚Üí novels |\n| name | varchar UNIQUE per novel |\n| aliases | jsonb (default []) |\n| gender | varchar? |\n| personality_traits | jsonb |\n| description | text? |\n| **tts_voice** | varchar (default af_heart) |\n| **voice_category** | varchar? |\n| first_appearance_chapter_id | FK ‚Üí novel_chapters? |\n| is_protagonist | bool |\n| **avatar_url** | text? |\n| avatar_prompt | text? |\n| avatar_generated_at | timestamp? |\n| profile_data | jsonb |\n| created_at | timestamp |\n| updated_at | timestamp |\n\n**Voice categories:**\n`young_female` ‚Üí af_bella\n`mature_female` ‚Üí af_heart\n`young_male` ‚Üí am_puck\n`mature_male` ‚Üí am_michael\n`old_male` ‚Üí am_fenrir  `narrator` ‚Üí af_heart","x":0,"y":20,"width":380,"height":620,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"t-appearances","type":"text","text":"## `chapter_character_appearances`\n\n| Column | Type |\n|--------|------|\n| id | bigint PK |\n| **chapter_id** | FK ‚Üí novel_chapters |\n| **character_id** | FK ‚Üí novel_characters |\n| is_new_appearance | bool |\n| created_at | timestamp |\n| updated_at | timestamp |\n\n---\nCreated by **Pipeline 1**.\nScopes LLM context for **Pipeline 2** ‚Äî only 5‚Äì20 characters per chapter sent to dialogue LLM, not all 200+ in the novel.","x":440,"y":20,"width":360,"height":320,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"t-tts","type":"text","text":"## `chapter_tts`\n\n| Column | Type |\n|--------|------|\n| id | bigint PK |\n| **chapter_id** | FK ‚Üí novel_chapters |\n| model | varchar (kokoro-82m) |\n| **voice** | varchar ‚Äî `af_heart` OR `'multi'` |\n| speed | decimal(3,2) |\n| audio_url | text? (S3 pre-signed, 7d TTL) |\n| audio_key | varchar? |\n| duration_seconds | decimal? |\n| **paragraph_timings** | jsonb ‚Üê see structure below |\n| url_expires_at | timestamp? |\n| **status** | enum pending/generating/complete/failed |\n| paragraphs_processed | uint |\n| paragraphs_total | uint |\n| error_message | text? |\n| created_at | timestamp |\n| updated_at | timestamp |\n\n**`paragraph_timings` JSON structure:**\n```\n[\n  {\n    start: 0.0, end: 13.8,\n    segments: [\n      {\n        segment_id: 3784,  ‚Üê llm_processed_paragraphs.id\n        voice: \"am_puck\",\n        is_dialogue: true,\n        split_order: 0,\n        alignment: [{word, start, end}],\n        character_id: 26   ‚Üê injected at read-time\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n]\n```\n`character_id` is NOT stored ‚Äî joined from\n`llm_processed_paragraphs.speaker_id` by `enrichTimingsWithCharacters()`","x":860,"y":20,"width":460,"height":620,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"t-pipeline-runs","type":"text","text":"## `chapter_pipeline_runs`\n\n| Column | Type |\n|--------|------|\n| id | bigint PK |\n| **chapter_id** | FK UNIQUE ‚Üí novel_chapters |\n| overall_status | enum pending/running/complete/failed |\n| run_count | uint |\n| scrape_status | varchar |\n| scrape_error | text? |\n| scrape_started_at / scrape_completed_at | timestamp? |\n| preprocess_status | varchar |\n| preprocess_error | text? |\n| preprocess_started_at / preprocess_completed_at | timestamp? |\n| characters_status | varchar |\n| characters_error | text? |\n| characters_started_at / characters_completed_at | timestamp? |\n| dialogue_status | varchar |\n| dialogue_error | text? |\n| dialogue_started_at / dialogue_completed_at | timestamp? |\n| narrative_status | varchar |\n| narrative_error | text? |\n| narrative_started_at / narrative_completed_at | timestamp? |\n| tts_status | varchar |\n| tts_error | text? |\n| tts_started_at / tts_completed_at | timestamp? |\n| created_at | timestamp |\n| updated_at | timestamp |\n\n*Stage status values: `pending` / `running` / `complete` / `failed` / `skipped`*\n*Narrative failure is non-blocking ‚Äî doesn't affect overall_status*","x":1380,"y":20,"width":680,"height":620,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"display-flutter","type":"text","text":"## üì± Flutter Reader\n`GET /api/chapters/{id}/paragraphs`\n\n**Text shown**: `processed_content` (mapped to `'content'`)\n‚Üí The LLM segment text is **never directly displayed**\n\n**Character tokens** (inline avatars):\n`chapter_tts.paragraph_timings[].segments[].segment_id`\n‚Üí `enrichTimingsWithCharacters()` joins ‚Üí `speaker_id`\n‚Üí `novel_characters.avatar_url`\n\n**Word highlighting**: word alignment timestamps from TTS\n\n**Table rows**: received as `is_table_row: true` but currently rendered as plain text paragraphs (same `content` string)\n\n‚öÝÔ∏è Admin shows LLM-split text; Flutter shows the original unsplit `processed_content` paragraph","x":0,"y":740,"width":520,"height":320,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"display-admin","type":"text","text":"## üñ• Admin Pipeline Viewer\n`GET /api/admin/chapters/{id}/pipeline`\n\n**Column 1 ‚Äî Raw**: `raw_content`\n**Column 2 ‚Äî Processed**: `processed_content`\n**Column 3 ‚Äî LLM**: `llm_processed_paragraphs.content`\n‚Üí Shows SPLIT text (dialogue vs attribution as separate rows)\n‚Üí Shows speaker name + voice\n‚Üí Shows is_dialogue / is_narration badge\n\n**Why text looks different vs Flutter:**\nIf LLM splits `\"Move out!\" Griff said.` into:\n- Segment 0: `\"Move out!\"` (dialogue, Griff)\n- Segment 1: `Griff said.` (narration)\n‚Üí Admin shows 2 rows; Flutter shows 1 paragraph","x":580,"y":740,"width":520,"height":320,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"display-tts","type":"text","text":"## üîä TTS Multi-Voice\n`POST /api/admin/chapters/{id}/tts` ‚Üí `GenerateChapterTts`\n\n**Input** (if `llm_processing_status = complete`):\n`llm_processed_paragraphs.content` per segment\n‚Üí Each LLM row = one audio segment with its own voice\n‚Üí `speaker.tts_voice` sent to Kokoro\n‚Üí `segment_id` echoed back in timing callback\n\n**Input** (if LLM not done):\n`processed_content` as single-voice paragraphs\n‚Üí No dialogue splitting, narrator voice only\n\n**Output stored** in `chapter_tts.paragraph_timings`\n‚Üí `segment_id` links back to `llm_processed_paragraphs`\n‚Üí `character_id` joined at read-time by API","x":1160,"y":740,"width":520,"height":320,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"note-discrepancy","type":"text","text":"## ‚öÝÔ∏è Key Discrepancy\n\nThe text Flutter displays and the text the TTS reads are **from different sources**:\n\n| Source | Text |\n|--------|------|\n| Flutter display | `processed_content` (original para) |\n| TTS audio | `llm_processed_paragraphs.content` (LLM split) |\n| Word highlight | Aligned to TTS audio segments |\n\nIf LLM rewrites/splits text, the word highlight anchors may drift from the displayed text.\n\nAlso: `is_table_row` paragraphs in Flutter are currently plain text ‚Äî no table rendering.","x":1700,"y":740,"width":360,"height":320,"color":"5"}
	],
	"edges":[
